Package datastructures.lists

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    List<T>
    A LinearList is a linear ADT which inserts elements in O(n), deletes them in O(n) and access them in O(n).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayListBasedList<T>
    ArrayListBasedList is a LinearList which is implemented with an ArrayList.
    DoublyLinkedList<T>
    A DoublyLinkedList is a LinkedList whose nodes have two references, one pointing to the previous and one to the next node.
    LinkedList<T>
    LinkedList is a simple (single) linked list.
    StaticArrayList<T>
    StaticArrayList is an implementation of a LinearList with an array.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EmptyListException  
    IllegalListAccessException
